			<h3>Challenge 路 Creating a custom parsing algorithm for entries</h3>

			<p class="project-description">
			The key challenge in this project was creating a database that would feed the right type of data to the word cloud.  
			
			</p>
			<br>
			<p class="project-description">I created an efficient algorithm that would take any entry (ie, a word or a phrase) and insert unique words into MongoDB once, while increasing the count of repeat words. The count of each word would then correspond to the font-size of each word rendered in the word cloud through D3. Upon inserting each unique word, I gave it a unique color based on Nielsen branding.
			</p>
